The evidence with the title 'The U.S. government is about to get hit with 'the perfect storm' of ... ' says May 12, 2010  ... Reinforcing the point , to address concerns stirred by a Congressional Budget Office ( CBO ) forecast that the U.S. government will accumulate total deficits in excess of $6 trillion over the next decade, in february president Obama issued an executive order to create a bipartisan fiscal commission . 
